sms,provides,text,messaging,services,for,businesses,of,all,sizes,Services,include,one,way,and,two,way,messaging,pager,replacement,long,messaging,reporting,and,more,sms,offers,an,API,that,allows,developers,to,integrate,messaging,services,into,their,applications,The,API,exposes,the,SMS,gateway,and,is,available,as,in,both,RESTful,and,SOAP,versions